data.description: Holy View!!!!   791 Youngstown Ridge Road featuring many recent updates thru-out, charming details and country living! You will love the recently completed basement remodel with all new luxury vinyl plank flooring in a weathered grey "wood-like" finish.  There is also a bar area with a refrigerator (+ plumbing for future sink, if desired) & an extra room that could be an at home office, den or a fitness room.  Other updates include: a metal roof, hot water heater 2022, heat pump/Central Air, & new hardwood floors in family room, new ceramic tile in main bathroom. Double closets + a 1/2 bath in the Master Bedroom, 1 car attached garage + ample extra parking in over-sized driveway, 2 large sheds + firewood storage too. You'll feel like your on vacation but yet close to all major routes! This is a MUST see!
